HEADWORD: Initials
<hw>In*i"tials</hw>, <pos>n. pl.</pos> <def>The first letters of a
person's first and last name, and sometimes also the first letters of
the middle name or names; <as>as, sign your <ex>initials</ex> in the
margin; people identified only by their
<ex>initials</ex></as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

